temp <- inner_join(
  df_dropout |>
    filter( %in% c('')) |>
    group_by() |>
    summarise( = sum(),
               = sum()) |>
    mutate( =  / sum()),
  df_dropout |> 
    filter( %in% c('', '')) |>
    group_by() |>
    summarise( = sum(),
               = sum()) |>
    mutate( =  / sum()),
  by = '') |>
  mutate(delta = abs(.x - .y), 
         position = ifelse(.x < .y, 
                        .x + (.y - .x) / 2, 
                        .y + (.x - .y) / 2
                        )
  )

temp |>
  ggplot(aes(y = )) +
  geom_segment(aes(x = .x, xend = .y, yend = ), 
               color = ifelse(temp$.x > temp$.y, 'dark red', 'dark cyan')) +
  geom_point(aes(x = .x, color = '')) +
  geom_point(aes(x = .y, color = 'KY')) +
  geom_text(aes(x = .x, label = scales::percent(.x, accuracy = 0.01)), 
            color = 'dark red', 
            vjust = -0.5,
            hjust = ifelse(temp$.x > temp$.y, 0, 1)) +
  geom_text(aes(x = .y, label = scales::percent(.y, accuracy = 0.01)), 
            color = 'dark cyan', 
            vjust = -0.5, 
            hjust = ifelse(temp$.y > temp$.x, 0, 1)) +
  geom_text(aes(x = position, 
                label = scales::percent(delta, accuracy = 0.01, suffix = '%p')), 
            vjust = 1.2) +
  scale_x_continuous(labels = scales::percent, expand = c(0.001, 0.001)) +
  scale_color_manual(name = '', values = c('' = 'dark red', 'KY' = 'dark cyan')) +
  labs(x = '   ', caption = '  : ')  +
theme(text = element_text(size=25))
